import React, { Component } from 'react' export default class About extends Component { render() { return (
About Us

Who Am I?

Detail-oriented professional with 17.5+ years of experience and a proven knowledge of IT strategy and project lifecycle. Aiming to leverage my skills to successfully fill the Product Manager role at your company.

I have started reflecting my ideas and thougths through the medium of words recently so spelling and grammer mistaks are very often.You can write me back if you spot any and don't want to live anymore :P

What I do?

Here are some of my expertise

Product Management

• Drive product planning and execution throughout the Product Lifecycle, including gathering and prioritizing product and customer requirements

Presales Solution Consultant

• Presales ITSM Consultant supporting pre-sales activities during RFP, RFI, RFX Analysis, Proposal and, Bid Management with Multi-Million TCV's for Customers Globally in a Multicultural working environment

Service Management

• Defining required ITIL processes by implementing processes, training and socializing / supporting employee adoption and usage of the service management processes such as incident, problem, change, event, request, CMDB

Dev Ops

Jenkins , Kubernetes , Docker

Graphic Design

My friend knows .. P

Digital Marketing

I use Instagram eight hours a day :)

) } }
